                      </figure>
        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ars-Technica-Chevrolet-Silverado-EV-11-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ars-Technica-Chevrolet-Silverado-EV-11.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ars-Technica-Chevrolet-Silverado-EV-11-980x653.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ars-Technica-Chevrolet-Silverado-EV-11-1440x960.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2026219">
          <figure style="height:653px;">
            <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Ars-Technica-Chevrolet-Silverado-EV-11-980x653.jpg'); background-color:#000"></div>
                          <figcaption id="caption-2026219">
                <span class="icon caption-arrow icon-drop-indicator"></span>
                                  <div class="caption">
                    There are a whole range of towing assists.                  </div>
